{"bangumi":{"date":"2006-04-04","platform":"TV","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/3c/ec/247_MnPPU.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/3c/ec/247_MnPPU.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/3c/ec/247_MnPPU.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/3c/ec/247_MnPPU.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/3c/ec/247_MnPPU.jpg"},"summary":"　　江户时代末期（本作的20年前）, 被称为“天人（あまんと）”的谜之异星人来袭。于是地球人与天人之间的战争瞬即爆发，为数众多的武士和攘夷派志士都参与与天人的战斗，幕府见识到天人强大的实力后，最终向天人低头，放弃武士不管，擅自与天人签订不平等条约，准许他们入国。其后更颁布了“废刀令”，夺走了武士的刀，使他们无力反抗。自此，天人横行霸道，幕府为天人所影响，甚至被控制，成为了“傀儡政权”。在这样的时代，有一个武士与同伴愉快地过著异想天开的生活。","name":"銀魂","name_cn":"银魂","tags":[{"name":"银他妈","count":3113,"total_cont":0},{"name":"吐槽","count":2701,"total_cont":0},{"name":"银魂","count":2327,"total_cont":0},{"name":"搞笑","count":1909,"total_cont":0},{"name":"JUMP","count":1570,"total_cont":0},{"name":"恶搞","count":1163,"total_cont":0},{"name":"銀魂~搞笑才是人生~","count":889,"total_cont":0},{"name":"GINTAMA","count":872,"total_cont":0},{"name":"TV","count":818,"total_cont":0},{"name":"SUNRISE","count":813,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2006","count":583,"total_cont":0},{"name":"天然卷发","count":537,"total_cont":0},{"name":"漫画改","count":470,"total_cont":0},{"name":"銀魂","count":331,"total_cont":0},{"name":"kuso","count":263,"total_cont":0},{"name":"钉宫","count":231,"total_cont":0},{"name":"假发","count":217,"total_cont":0},{"name":"战斗","count":190,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2006年4月","count":184,"total_cont":0},{"name":"杉田智和","count":164,"total_cont":0},{"name":"漫改","count":148,"total_cont":0},{"name":"热血","count":146,"total_cont":0},{"name":"喜剧","count":142,"total_cont":0},{"name":"土银","count":124,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日本","count":118,"total_cont":0},{"name":"S田","count":100,"total_cont":0},{"name":"灵魂支柱","count":81,"total_cont":0},{"name":"科幻","count":81,"total_cont":0},{"name":"高松信司","count":80,"total_cont":0},{"name":"人生的意义","count":80,"total_cont":0}],"infobox":[{"key":"中文名","value":"银魂"},{"key":"话数","value":"20